Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.86.0:00:40.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}"BIG WAYNE SLAMMER.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:40.59.0:00:43.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}COMES WITH POSABLE\NNECK-SMASH GRIP."
Dialogue: 0.0:00:43.63.0:00:44.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THAT'S PRETTY COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:44.93.0:00:46.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(90.408)}LET'S SEE...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:46.23.0:00:47.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(450.432)}COCK !
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.70.0:00:51.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}"THE BLACK JACKAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:51.00.0:00:53.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}KARATE-KICK POWER FORCE\NAND BENDABLE NECK."
Dialogue: 0.0:00:53.17.0:00:54.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(378.432)}ASSHOLE. COCK !
Dialogue: 0.0:00:57.07.0:00:58.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ASSHOLE. SHIT.\NSHIT. COCK !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:00.11.0:01:01.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}MA'AM. IS THAT\NYOUR SON OVER THERE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:01.84.0:01:03.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}YES. I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:03.15.0:01:05.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}MY SON HAS\NTOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:05.32.0:01:06.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}TOURETTE'S SYNDROME ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.62.0:01:08.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}IT'S A NEUROLOGICAL DISORDER.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.35.0:01:10.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}HE CAN'T CONTROL\NWHAT HE SAYS.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:10.52.0:01:11.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}OH.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.39.0:01:12.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:12.69.0:01:13.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.408)}DUMB SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:13.99.0:01:15.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ALL RIGHT. THOMAS.\NMAYBE WE SHOULD GO ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:15.73.0:01:16.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}ALL RIGHT. MOM.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:16.59.0:01:17.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.408)}BITCH. ASS. BITCH !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:17.89.0:01:20.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HERE. LET'S BUY YOU\NA NICE TOY TO TAKE HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:22.67.0:01:23.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}DUDE. THAT MOM IS COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:26.57.0:01:28.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}COCK NUT. UGH...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.74.0:01:30.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.408)}STUPID SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:30.47.0:01:32.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ARE YOU TALKING TO ME ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.21.0:01:33.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}NO... COCK NOSE !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:33.94.0:01:35.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}WHAT'S YOUR PROBLEM. KID ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:35.68.0:01:36.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}OH. I'M SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:36.98.0:01:39.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}\h\hMY SON THOMAS HAS\NTOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:39.15.0:01:40.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}WHAT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:40.45.0:01:41.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}MOM. LET'S JUST GO.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:41.32.0:01:42.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(468.432)}SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.62.0:01:44.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}\h\h\hPEOPLE WITH TOURETTE'S\NCAN'T CONTROL CERTAIN TICKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.35.0:01:46.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}IT'S LIKE A SNEEZE.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:46.09.0:01:48.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(324.432)}ASSHOLE. ASSHOLE !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.26.0:01:51.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}WAIT. WAIT. WAIT.\NWHOA. WHOA. WHOA.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:51.29.0:01:52.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}YOU'RE TELLING ME\NTHERE'S AN ILLNESS
Dialogue: 0.0:01:52.60.0:01:53.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THAT MAKES YOU BLURT OUT\NOBSCENITIES ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.90.0:01:55.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}MOM. CAN WE JUST\NGO HOME PLEASE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:55.63.0:01:57.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}IT'S OKAY. THOMAS.\N\hTHEY UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:57.37.0:01:59.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(396.432)}I WANT TO GO !
Dialogue: 0.0:01:59.54.0:02:00.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(432.408)}SHIT. FAG !
Dialogue: 0.0:02:00.84.0:02:03.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hPOOR KID.\NYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.44.0:02:05.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}ALL RIGHT. HOLD ON\NJUST A SECOND HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:05.17.0:02:07.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(90.432)}ARE YOU TELLING ME THAT IF YOU\N\hHAVE THIS TOURETTE'S SYNDROME
Dialogue: 0.0:02:07.78.0:02:09.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}YOU CAN SAY WHATEVER\NYOU WANT ALL THE TIME
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.95.0:02:10.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}AND NEVER GET IN TROUBLE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:11.25.0:02:12.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}IT'S A NEUROLOGICAL DISORDER.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:12.98.0:02:14.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HE CAN'T HELP IT.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hYEAH.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:16.45.0:02:17.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}( ding )
Dialogue: 0.0:02:18.62.0:02:22.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.144)}\h\h\h( Cartman )\N\h\h\h♪ I'VE GOT\NA GOLDEN TICKET ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:02:22.53.0:02:26.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.120)}♪ I'VE GOT A GOLDEN TWINKLE\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hIN MY EYE ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:02:26.43.0:02:28.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}( laughing )
Dialogue: 0.0:02:28.16.0:02:29.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HEY. DON'T YOU\NWANNA BUY THAT TOY ?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:29.90.0:02:31.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}I DON'T NEED THE TOY !
Dialogue: 0.0:02:31.20.0:02:32.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}\h\h\h\hI'VE FOUND\NSOMETHING BETTER !
Dialogue: 0.0:02:32.50.0:02:35.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}♪ 'CAUSE I'VE GOT\NA GOLDEN TICKET ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:02:35.97.0:02:39.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}♪ I'VE GOT A GOLDEN CHANCE\N\h\h\h\h\hTO MAKE MY WAY ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.25.0:02:49.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}IT STARTED ABOUT\NFOUR DAYS AGO. DOCTOR.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.42.0:02:51.59.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}AND EVERY DAY HE SEEMS\NTO GET WORSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.59.0:02:53.32.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}P-P-PUSSY. PUSSY !
Dialogue: 0.0:02:53.32.0:02:54.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCOCK. SHIT !\NOH. DEAR.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:54.62.0:02:56.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}I WAS CHECKING OUT\NTHE INTERNET.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:56.36.0:02:58.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}AND IT ALMOST\NSEEMS LIKE HIS SYMPTOMS
Dialogue: 0.0:02:58.53.0:02:59.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ARE LIKE THOSE IN\NSOMETHING CALLED
Dialogue: 0.0:03:00.26.0:03:02.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}"TOURETTE'S SYNDROME."
Dialogue: 0.0:03:02.43.0:03:04.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}TOURETTE'S SYNDROME ?\NWHAT IS THAT. MOMMY ?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:04.60.0:03:06.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}BUTTHOLE. TITTIES. BALLS !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:06.34.0:03:08.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}THAT DOESN'T SEEM LIKELY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.50.0:03:10.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.432)}TOURETTE'S IS\NA HEREDITARY DISEASE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.67.0:03:11.97.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(378.432)}IT DOESN'T JUST\NSUDDENLY START.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:13.71.0:03:15.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.432)}COCKSUCKER.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:16.75.0:03:18.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}ON THE OTHER HAND. TOURETTE'S\NDOES OFTEN DEVELOP
Dialogue: 0.0:03:18.92.0:03:22.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}LATER IN A CHILD'S LIFE.\NGETTING PROGRESSIVELY WORSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:22.39.0:03:23.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}OH. WELL. THAT'S IT !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:23.69.0:03:25.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.408)}SHITHEAD. ASSHOLE !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:25.42.0:03:26.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}MEXICAN STINKY BALLS !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:26.72.0:03:28.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}OH. DOCTOR.\NCAN YOU HELP HIM ?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.46.0:03:31.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}WE DON'T KNOW VERY MUCH\NABOUT TOURETTE'S I'M AFRAID.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.06.0:03:33.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}BUT WE WILL GET YOUR SON\NALL THE HELP WE CAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:33.66.0:03:35.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}BUT WHAT ABOUT SCHOOL.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDOCTOR ?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.40.0:03:36.70.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}THE TEACHERS. THE PRINCIPAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:36.70.0:03:38.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}THEY WON'T UNDERSTAND THAT\NI CAN'T CONTROL WHAT I SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:38.87.0:03:40.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}DON'T WORRY. YOUNG MAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:40.60.0:03:42.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}WE'LL MAKE SURE EVERYONE\NUNDERSTANDS YOUR DISEASE
Dialogue: 0.0:03:42.77.0:03:44.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}AND GIVES YOU THE COMPASSION\NYOU DESERVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:44.94.0:03:46.24.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}OH. THAT'S AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:46.68.0:03:48.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.408)}THANK YOU-- FAGGOT !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.85.0:03:51.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}( school bell ringing )
Dialogue: 0.0:03:51.88.0:03:53.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.18.0:03:54.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.408)}BUTTHOLE !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:54.92.0:03:56.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.432)}HEY. WENDY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:56.22.0:03:57.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.408)}DUMB BITCH !
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.52.0:03:59.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.432)}OH. SORRY.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:59.26.0:04:01.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.408)}TITTIES. COCK !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:01.42.0:04:03.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}GINGER RETARD !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:03.16.0:04:04.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.408)}ASS-LICKER DICKFACE !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:04.46.0:04:05.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}DUDE. YOU BETTER\NWATCH IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:05.76.0:04:07.50.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THE PRINCIPAL'S\NRIGHT OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.50.0:04:09.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}\hOH. GOOD MORNING.\NPRINCIPAL VICTORIA.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:09.67.0:04:10.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}SHIT BALLS !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.97.0:04:12.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}GOOD MORNING. ERIC.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:14.44.0:04:16.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}DID CARTMAN JUST SAY\N"SHIT BALLS" TO THE PRINCIPAL ?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:16.61.0:04:17.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}YOU DIDN'T HEAR ?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.91.0:04:19.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}\h\h\h\h\hWELL. CARTMAN HAS\NSOME MENTAL DISEASE CALLED
Dialogue: 0.0:04:19.21.0:04:20.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}TOURETTE'S SYNDROME\N\h\h\hOR SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:20.94.0:04:21.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}WHAT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:22.25.0:04:23.55.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(270.432)}HE'S THE LUCKIEST KID\NIN THE WORLD.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:23.55.0:04:25.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}IF I COULD SAY\N"SHIT BALLS" TO THE PRINCIPAL.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:25.28.0:04:27.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}I'D BE SO HAPPY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:27.45.0:04:29.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}\h\h\hUH. EXCUSE ME.\NEXCUSE ME. EVERYONE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.19.0:04:31.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(90.432)}I GUESS YOU MIGHT HAVE NOTICED\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hMY AWKWARD TICKS.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:31.79.0:04:33.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}ASSHOLE !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:33.09.0:04:34.39.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}PUSSY. ASSHOLE !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:34.39.0:04:35.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}I-- UGH.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:35.69.0:04:37.43.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}\hI JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW\NTHAT I CAN'T CONTROL IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:37.43.0:04:38.73.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}IT'S OKAY. ERIC.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:38.73.0:04:41.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}WE ALL UNDERSTAND AND WE\NTHINK YOU'RE VERY BRAVE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.07.0:04:44.38.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HE'S FAKING.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:46.10.0:04:47.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}( chuckling )
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.84.0:04:49.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}\h\h\h\hEXCUSE ME. EVERYONE.\NI NEED TO HAVE A MOMENT ALONE
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.14.0:04:50.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}WITH MY GOOD FRIEND KYLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:50.87.0:04:51.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}ASS CHEEKS !
Dialogue: 0.0:04:53.48.0:04:55.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}KYLE. APPARENTLY YOU MISSED\NTHE SCHOOL ASSEMBLY YESTERDAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:55.65.0:04:56.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}BUT I'VE BEEN DIAGNOSED WITH
Dialogue: 0.0:04:56.51.0:04:58.25.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}A VERY SERIOUS\NMENTAL CONDITION.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:58.25.0:05:00.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}YOU DO NOT HAVE\NTOURETTE'S SYNDROME. FAT ASS.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.59.0:05:03.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}OH. OKAY.\NYOU FIGURED ME OUT.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:03.89.0:05:05.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}BRAVO. KYLE. BRAVO.
