Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.57.0:10:59.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h( Chris )\N\hBUT NOW WE'RE SWITCHING\NOUR FOCUS FROM PEDOPHILES
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.61.0:11:01.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}TO TOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:01.34.0:11:03.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(90.432)}IT ALL STARTED WHEN I RECEIVED\N\h\h\h\h\hTHIS TOUCHING LETTER
Dialogue: 0.0:11:03.51.0:11:06.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}\h\h\h\h\hFROM A BRAVE\NLITTLE BOY IN COLORADO.
