Dialogue: 0.0:11:10.45.0:11:12.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.120)}\h\h\h\h\h"WON'T YOU DO\NA SPECIAL REPORT ON {\i1}ME.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:12.19.0:11:13.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.120)}"SO THAT THE WORLD CAN\N\h\hLEARN TO {\i1}ACCEPT{\r} US
Dialogue: 0.0:11:13.92.0:11:15.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.96)}"INSTEAD OF JUST LAUGH ?
