Dialogue: 0.0:11:54.26.0:11:56.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THE FINAL COG\NIN MY MASTER PLAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:56.87.0:11:59.91.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THIS SATURDAY I WILL GO ON\NNATIONAL TELEVISION. LIVE.
