Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.32.0:15:35.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}UH. I NEED TO BE GOING NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.05.0:15:35.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ALL RIGHT. ERIC.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.92.0:15:38.95.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}WELL. GOOD LUCK\NON {\i1}DATELINE{\r} TONIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:39.39.0:15:40.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}{\i1}DATELINE.{\r} RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:40.69.0:15:42.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.408)}I WET MY BE-- AHH !
Dialogue: 0.0:15:42.42.0:15:44.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}\h\h\h\hI TOUCHED MY\NCOUSIN'S WIEN-- AHH !
Dialogue: 0.0:15:44.16.0:15:46.33.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}THIS SURE HAS BEEN FUN--\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hGOODBYE !
Dialogue: 0.0:15:46.33.0:15:48.06.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(432.432)}AGH !
Dialogue: 0.0:15:50.67.0:15:54.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}TONIGHT. AN INSIDE LOOK\NAT TOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:54.14.0:15:57.18.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}I'M CHRIS HANSEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:57.17.0:15:59.34.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.408)}I'M CHRIS HANSEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:59.34.0:16:01.94.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}UH. MR. HANSEN. I'M AFRAID\NI CAN'T DO THE SHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:01.94.0:16:03.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(432.432)}WHY NOT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:03.68.0:16:05.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}MY. UH. MY GRANDMA\NJUST DIED.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.85.0:16:07.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}SO I HAVE TO\NGO TO MEMPHIS.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:07.15.0:16:08.45.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THAT'S NOT TRUE !\NMY GRANDMA'S FINE !
Dialogue: 0.0:16:10.19.0:16:12.36.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}WHY DON'T YOU HAVE A SEAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:12.35.0:16:13.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}I JUST NEED\NTO GET HOME.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.66.0:16:14.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}I'M NOT DOING THE SHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:14.52.0:16:16.26.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}GO AHEAD AND TAKE A SEAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:16.26.0:16:17.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}BUT I'M NOT GONNA\NDO THE--\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hTAKE A SEAT\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hRIGHT OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:21.90.0:16:23.63.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.63.0:16:26.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}I'M-- I'M TELLING YOU THAT\NI'M NOT DOING THE SHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:26.24.0:16:27.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}BUT YOU ARE DOING THE SHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:27.97.0:16:29.27.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:29.27.0:16:31.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ALL OF A SUDDEN.\NI CAN'T CONTROL WHAT I SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:31.01.0:16:33.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(198.432)}WELL. OF COURSE YOU CAN'T\NCONTROL WHAT YOU SAY.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:33.18.0:16:34.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}YOU HAVE TOURETTE'S.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.48.0:16:35.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}NO. MY TOURETTE'S\NHAS GOTTEN WORSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:35.78.0:16:37.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}BEFORE I JUST BLURTED OUT\NCOOL STUFF
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.08.0:16:38.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ABOUT JEWS\NBEING LAME AND STUFF.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:38.81.0:16:40.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}BUT NOW IT'S GOTTEN\NREALLY BAD.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.12.0:16:42.29.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}SO I'M SORRY.\NBUT I'M NOT DOING THE SHOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.28.0:16:44.02.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THAT'S IT-- GOODBYE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:44.02.0:16:45.75.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}WHY DON'T YOU TAKE A SEAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.75.0:16:46.62.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}NO. I DON'T WANNA\NTAKE A SEAT.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.62.0:16:47.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hHAVE A SEAT.\NNO. I'M JUST GONNA GO--
Dialogue: 0.0:16:47.92.0:16:49.66.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}TAKE A SEAT\NRIGHT OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:51.39.0:16:53.56.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HOW DOES HE DO THAT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:53.56.0:16:55.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}YOU KNOW. ONE TIME I WAS\NDOING A SHOW CALLED
Dialogue: 0.0:16:55.30.0:16:57.03.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}"TO CATCH A PREDATOR."
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.03.0:16:57.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}WE ALMOST CAUGHT\NTHIS PEDOPHILE
Dialogue: 0.0:16:58.33.0:16:59.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}BUT THEN HE RAN FROM US
Dialogue: 0.0:16:59.20.0:17:00.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}BECAUSE HE DIDN'T\NWANNA BE ON {\i1}DATELINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:00.94.0:17:03.11.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}SO WE TRACKED HIM DOWN\NTO HIS HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.11.0:17:05.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.432)}AND YOU KNOW\NWHAT HE DID ?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:05.27.0:17:07.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}HE SHOT HIMSELF.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:07.44.0:17:11.78.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}IT'D BE A SHAME IF YOU\NDIDN'T WANNA GO ON {\i1}DATELINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:11.78.0:17:13.51.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}BE A SHAME IF WE HAD TO\NTRACK YOU DOWN
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.52.0:17:15.69.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}AND YOU "SHOT YOURSELF."
Dialogue: 0.0:17:17.85.0:17:19.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}I JUST PEED MY PANTS.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:23.16.0:17:25.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.144)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h( announcer )\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hLIVE. FROM OUR\NSATELLITE STUDIO IN COLORADO.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:25.76.0:17:27.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.96)}THIS IS {\i1}DATELINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.93.0:17:31.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}TONIGHT. AN INSIDE LOOK\NAT TOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:31.40.0:17:36.17.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}I'M CHRIS HANSEN.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.17.0:17:38.77.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}IN A FEW MINUTES. YOU WILL\NMEET LITTLE ERIC CARTMAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:38.77.0:17:41.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}WHO WANTS THE WORLD TO\NUNDERSTAND HIS AFFLICTION.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:41.81.0:17:42.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}( knocking )
Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.68.0:17:44.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(324.432)}( man )\NFIVE MINUTES. KID.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.85.0:17:47.01.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}\h\hJESUS CHRIST. HOW DID\NI GET MYSELF INTO THIS ?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:48.75.0:17:52.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}\h\h\hGOD... PLEASE.\NI KNOW I SCREWED UP.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:52.65.0:17:54.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}I SHOULD HAVE NEVER PRETENDED\NTO HAVE TOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.82.0:17:56.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}BUT. SEE. I GET IT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.99.0:17:59.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}YOU CAN'T JUST WALK AROUND\N\hSAYING WHATEVER YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:59.16.0:18:00.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}YOU GAVE US A FILTER
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.46.0:18:02.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}\h\hBECAUSE PEOPLE DON'T\NWANNA HEAR THINGS LIKE--
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.20.0:18:03.93.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}I TOUCHED PENISES\NWITH MY COUSIN !
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.93.0:18:05.67.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}AHH-AHH.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.67.0:18:07.84.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}AND I LEARNED YOU ESPECIALLY\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCAN'T SAY
Dialogue: 0.0:18:07.84.0:18:09.14.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}\h\h\hWHATEVER YOU WANT\NON NATIONAL TELEVISION.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.14.0:18:11.74.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}BECAUSE THERE COULD BE\N\h\h\h\hKIDS WATCHING.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.74.0:18:13.47.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(90.432)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hPLEASE. GOD.\NDON'T MAKE ME EMBARRASS MYSELF
Dialogue: 0.0:18:13.48.0:18:15.22.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}ON NATIONAL TELEVISION.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:15.21.0:18:18.68.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}\h\h\h\hYOU MUST SEE HOW THIS IS\NALL SOMEWHAT YOUR FAULT. RIGHT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.68.0:18:20.85.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}PLEASE... I NEED A MIRACLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:26.05.0:18:27.35.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}TANGO. THIS IS FOXTROT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:27.79.0:18:29.09.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.408)}ARE YOU IN POSITION ?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:29.09.0:18:32.13.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(324.432)}COPY. FOXTROT--\NTANGO IN POSITION.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:32.13.0:18:33.86.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.432)}AW. SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:18:33.86.0:18:35.16.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}YOU SURE YOU DON'T\NWANNA BACK OUT ?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.16.0:18:37.76.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}NO. NO. YOU WERE RIGHT.\NTHAT FAT KID IS FAKING IT.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:37.77.0:18:39.08.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(342.432)}IF HE GOES ON TV.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:39.07.0:18:40.80.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}MORE PEOPLE WILL THINK THAT\NHAVING TOURETTE'S IS FUN.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.80.0:18:42.10.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}ASSHOLE. SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:18:42.10.0:18:43.40.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}ALL RIGHT. THEN WE\NGO WITH THE PLAN.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.41.0:18:45.15.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}JUST LIKE\N"TO CATCH A PREDATOR."
Dialogue: 0.0:18:45.14.0:18:46.44.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THE FIRST GUY IS HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:46.44.0:18:48.61.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THIS IS PROBABLY\NHotForBoys219.
