Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.25.0:18:55.98.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}YEAH. I WAS CHATTING\NWITH YOU ON-LINE.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.98.0:18:57.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.432)}SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.29.0:18:59.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}OH. GOD. I'M SO\NTURNED ON RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:59.45.0:19:01.19.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}THIS IS YOUR HOUSE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:01.19.0:19:02.49.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}YOUR PARENTS AREN'T\NHOME ARE THEY ?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:02.49.0:19:03.79.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(234.432)}NO. IT'S COOL.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.79.0:19:05.53.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}GO ON INSIDE.\NI MADE BROWNIES.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:05.53.0:19:06.83.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.432)}SHIT !
Dialogue: 0.0:19:06.83.0:19:09.00.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}I'M JUST GONNA SLIP INTO\NSOMETHING MORE COMFORTABLE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.00.0:19:10.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(108.432)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCOCK !\NOKAY !
