Dialogue: 0.0:19:13.34.0:19:14.65.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(414.408)}( giggling )
Dialogue: 0.0:19:14.64.0:19:19.41.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}SO NOW LET'S MEET A CHILD\NWHO HAS TOURETTE'S SYNDROME.
