Dialogue: 0.0:19:21.58.0:19:22.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.408)}OH. OH.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:22.88.0:19:25.05.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}WAIT A MINUTE.\NTHIS AIN'T NO HOUSE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.48.0:19:27.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(288.432)}WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
