Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.82.0:19:32.42.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}OH. NO. IT'S A SETUP !\NI KNEW IT !
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.42.0:19:33.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(126.432)}SIR. WHY DON'T YOU\NTAKE A SEAT RIGHT OVER THERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:33.72.0:19:35.89.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}NOW EVERYONE'S\NGONNA KNOW I'M A PERV !
