Dialogue: 0.0:19:38.06.0:19:40.23.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(216.432)}( all screaming )
Dialogue: 0.0:19:40.23.0:19:41.96.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(378.432)}OH. NOT AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.57.0:19:45.87.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(162.432)}KYLE ?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:45.87.0:19:47.60.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(306.432)}SURPRISE. FAT ASS !
Dialogue: 0.0:19:47.60.0:19:48.90.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}KYLE. WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.90.0:19:50.20.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(378.432)}I WENT ON-LINE\NPOSING AS A BOY
Dialogue: 0.0:19:50.21.0:19:51.52.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(324.432)}WHO WOULD HAVE SEX\NWITH OLDER MEN
Dialogue: 0.0:19:51.51.0:19:52.81.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(360.432)}AND TOLD THEM\NTO MEET ME HERE.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.81.0:19:54.54.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}MY PLAN WORKED PERFECTLY !
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.54.0:19:56.28.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(180.432)}( car horns honking )
