Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.75.0:20:01.92.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.408)}\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hHA-HA.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hWHOO-HOO.\NHA-HA.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hCHILDREN.
