Dialogue: 0.0:20:03.65.0:20:05.82.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(72.432)}HEY. I BROUGHT YOU\NSOME {\i1}WENDY'S.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:05.82.0:20:07.99.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(144.432)}\h\hYEAH. YEAH. GO ON IN.\NTHERE'S A HOT TUB INSIDE.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:07.99.0:20:09.72.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}STUPID SHIT !
