Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.71.0:20:34.88.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(252.432)}( screaming )
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.18.0:20:37.48.Default..0.0.0..{\an1\pos(468.432)}HEY !
